        <div class="content-body mb-5">
          <h1 class="page-title-2 text-center">
            BURSA FAIR CENTER (BFC)
          </h1>
          <h4>
            Restaurants and Cafes
          </h4>
          <p>
            At the Bursa Fair Center, the comfort of our visitors and exhibitors is our top priority.
            Restaurants and cafes located within the fairgrounds offer all your food and beverage needs throughout the
            day.
          </p>
          <h4>
            Restaurant Area
          </h4>
          <p>
            Offering a wide range of dishes, including traditional Turkish cuisine, international menus, and freshly
            prepared dishes daily, it offers an ideal setting for lunches, meeting breaks, and events.
          </p>
          <h4>
            Cafe Areas
          </h4>
          <p>
            Located at the foyer and hall entrances, cafes offer visitors a pleasant break with a variety of hot and
            cold beverages, desserts, and snacks.
          </p>
          <h4>
            Comfort and Fast Service
          </h4>
          <p>
            With their modern design, spacious seating areas, and fast service, restaurants and cafes aim to make
            your trade fair experience more comfortable and productive.
          </p>
          <h4>
            Event Support Services
          </h4>
          <p>
            Group catering, cocktails, and special menu services are also provided as needed, meeting the demands of
            participating companies and organizers.
            <br />
            In short, our guests at the Bursa Fair Center can enjoy both their business meetings and social breaks by
            taking advantage of quality food and beverage services throughout the event.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
